      • setValueRange

        public void setValueRange(int axisIndex,
                          java.lang.Double minimum,
                          java.lang.Double maximum,
                          java.lang.Double majorUnit,
                          java.lang.Double minorUnit)
        Set value range (basic Axis Options)(设置值范围（基本轴选项）)
        Parameters:
        axisIndex - 0 - primary axis, 1 - secondary axis(axisIndex - 0 -主轴，1 -次轴)
        minimum - minimum value; Double.NaN - automatic; null - no change(minimum -最小值; Double.NaN -自动;空-无更改)
        maximum - maximum value; Double.NaN - automatic; null - no change(max-最大值; Double.NaN -自动;空-无更改)
        majorUnit - major unit value; Double.NaN - automatic; null - no change(majorUnit -主要单位值; Double.NaN -自动;空-无更改)
        minorUnit - minor unit value; Double.NaN - automatic; null - no change(minorUnit -次要单位值; Double.NaN -自动;空-无更改)
